data.description: Welcome to 1589 Lewes Castle Dr, located in Sussex Place. This property presents an exceptional opportunity to own a stunning home in Grove City. With its modern design, contemporary features, and prime location close to shopping & highway access, this residence offers the perfect blend of comfort and style. As you step foot in this home, you will be greeted with a large entryway that leads to the heart of the house. The spacious and open floor plan allows for seamless flow and abundant natural light throughout. The main level features a spacious living room & Fireplace, providing an inviting space to relax or entertain guests. Large Kitchen Island, granite countertops and eat in kitchen space. Head upstairs to large owner suite as well as second floor laundry.
